# ThuChi365 - Laravel + Filament v4

## Framework & Tools
- Laravel latest LTS
- Filament v4.1+
- Spatie Laravel Permission
- PHP 8.2+

## Code Style
- PSR-12
- Use type hints
- Vietnamese labels for UI
- English for code/comments

## Database
- Use migrations
- Index important columns
- Use decimal(15,2) for money
- Timezone: Asia/Ho_Chi_Minh

## Filament
- Use Filament v4 syntax
- Resources in app/Filament/Resources
- Policies for permissions
- Vietnamese labels

## Permissions
- Admin: full access
- Manager: limited (same day only)
- Employee: create income, view own stats

## Naming
- Models: singular (Employee, Income, Expense)
- Tables: plural (employees, incomes, expenses)
- Vietnamese for user-facing text

